        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asking aid in correcting false statements.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Mr L R Kenny</persName></p>
<p>Dear sir</p>

<p>I saw a few lines written By <persName>coln Austin</persName> to <persName>Mr Warren</persName> 
informing him his petition could not Be Received I think that their
Has Been some false and malisious statements made against <persName>Mr
Warren </persName>and I wish you would Enquire in to it and iff so you will
assist Him as a friend and it will accomodate yours with Respect</p>

<p><persName>John W Hall</persName></p>


        </div1>
